[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1129","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1129.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1482","title":"SVGAlib zgv 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SVGAlib zgv 3.0-7 及更早版本存在权限泄露漏洞。zgv 是一款基于 SVGAlib 的图像查看工具，在处理子进程时未能正确隔离 iopl(3) 特权级别，导致本地攻击者可通过执行子进程继承父进程的 I/O 特权，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Linux 系统上使用 SVGAlib zgv 的环境，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1482"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.183","remediation":"升级 SVGAlib zgv 至 3.0-8 或更高版本，该版本修复了 iopl(3) 权限泄漏至子进程的问题。如无法升级，可移除 zgv 软件包或限制本地用户执行 setuid 二进制程序作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=1999-02-15&msg=Pine.LNX.3.96.990219175605.9622A-100000%40ferret.lmh.ox.ac.uk"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1129.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0158","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0158.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0485","title":"OpenBSD 2.4 ipintr 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核网络协议栈中的 ipintr() 函数在处理 IP 碎片重组队列（ipq）时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形 IP 数据包触发该漏洞，导致内核崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，但需要一定的网络条件。CVSS v2 评分为 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0485"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-19","updated":"1999-02-19","remediation":"立即升级到 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本。如无法升级，请为 OpenBSD 2.4 依次安装 maxqueue 补丁、tcp decoding 补丁和 ipintr 补丁（编号 006），补丁可从 ftp.openbsd.org/pub/OpenBSD/patches/2.4/common/ 获取。也可在边界防火墙上限制对受影响主机的 IP 分片流量作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0158.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0050","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0405","title":"Linux Lsof 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞","description":"Lsof（List Open Files）工具在处理超长命令行参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码。受影响系统包括 Debian 2.0、FreeBSD 3.2、OpenBSD 2.4、RedHat 5.2 及 SuSE 6.1 等版本，危害等级高。攻击者需具备目标系统的本地访问权限，即通过本地账号登录后运行特制的 lsof 命令即可触发漏洞，无需额外认证条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0405"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.623","remediation":"tags. The user asked for the answer to be between <value> and","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3163","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19374","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0405.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0405","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0405.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0405.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72r6-cpj9-gh8x/GHSA-72r6-cpj9-gh8x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--3d8f7267-453f-418a-8f3b-092d47e9d29f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1133","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1133.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1495","title":"SuSE Linux xtvscreen 符号链接攻击致任意文件写入漏洞","description":"SuSE Linux 6.0 中的 xtvscreen 程序存在任意文件写入漏洞。本地攻击者可通过符号链接攻击方式，在目标系统上创建指向 pic000.pnm 文件的符号链接，当 xtvscreen 程序运行时将覆盖链接指向的任意文件，导致系统文件被破坏或敏感数据被篡改。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者拥有本地用户权限，危害等级较低，CVSS 评分 2.1。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1495"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.817","remediation":"立即升级 SuSE Linux 至 7.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 xtvscreen 的符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，可移除 xtvscreen 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xtvscreen）或直接删除该程序以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12580","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/325","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1792"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1133.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0913","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1060","title":"Tetrix TetriNet 守护进程缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Tetrix TetriNet 后台守护进程 1.13.16 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过连接该服务监听的 31457 端口，并提供一个超长的 DNS 主机名触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 TetriNet 1.13.16 及可能更早的版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1060"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.310","remediation":"升级 tetrinetx 到已应用补丁的版本（>1.13.16），或将 UHOSTLEN 从 30 改为 256，将 main.c 中栈缓冲区从 121 改为 UHOSTLEN，并将 net.c 中的 strcpy 替换为 strncpy。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 TCP 31457 端口的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91937090211855&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/340","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1060","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a35e01f-9c82-4365-a727-7af8d726e1c6.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000529.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0913.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1405","title":"IBM AIX snap 不安全的临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 及之前版本中的 snap 命令存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞。snap 命令在执行时会在 /tmp 目录下创建 ibmsupt 目录，且该目录权限设置为全局可读。当以 root 权限执行 snap -a 命令时，系统不会清理或删除该临时目录。本地攻击者可通过在 root 执行 snap -a 之前，在 /tmp/ibmsupt/general/ 目录下预先创建恶意的 passwd 文件，从而劫持系统密码文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3.2 之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1405"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:22.220","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.3.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 snap 命令的临时文件竞争条件漏洞。如无法升级，可手动在 /tmp/ibmsupt 目录创建后立即设置 0700 权限，或使用 chmod 命令限制其可读性；同时建议使用专用临时目录并配置 umask 077 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91936783009385&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91954824614013&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/375","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19300","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1405","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1405.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gcvv-4h27-hqp8/GHSA-gcvv-4h27-hqp8.json","https://github.com/lcashdol/advisories/blob/32733f854e018593b94f048e59ce3442a76d2767/advisory-9.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1405.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/375/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a32a8be3-115e-4d1a-b931-1ab3b612dbd1.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0042","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0042.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0396","title":"NetBSD/OpenBSD TCP服务器 select/accept 竞争条件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"NetBSD和OpenBSD系统的TCP服务器在处理select()和accept()系统调用时存在竞争条件漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用该竞争条件，在特定时间窗口内发送精心构造的网络请求，导致服务器进程进入死锁状态或崩溃，从而造成拒绝服务。攻击条件较为苛刻，需要精确的时间控制，攻击复杂度较高。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0396"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"OpenBSD用户应应用errata 002补丁或升级至OpenBSD 2.4及以上版本；NetBSD用户应升级至1999年2月8日之后的内核版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制对TCP服务的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0396","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0396","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0396.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6hqw-w28m-789c/GHSA-6hqw-w28m-789c.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0042.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0374","title":"Debian GNU/Linux cfengine 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 发行版中的 cfengine 软件包存在符号链接攻击漏洞。cfengine 是一款基于主机的配置管理工具，通常以 root 权限运行。由于其在处理临时文件时未充分验证符号链接的真实性，拥有本地账户权限的攻击者可通过在可写目录中创建恶意符号链接（指向 /etc/shadow 等系统关键文件），诱导 cfengine 以 root 权限错误地读取或覆写目标文件，导致敏感信息泄露或系统完整性破坏。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0374"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.563","remediation":"建议升级 cfengine 至 1.5.4 及以上版本，该版本修复了临时文件创建中的符号链接跟随漏洞。使用 cfengine 管理文件时避免将临时文件写入公共可写目录（如 /tmp），或使用专属临时目录并设置 umask 077 限制访问权限。在 Debian 系统中及时应用 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade 保持软件包更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0374"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1180","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e 及 Website Pro 2.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 args.cmd 或 args.bat 参数传递 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号等）执行任意系统命令。由于服务器未对用户输入做有效过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害较大。该漏洞影响 O'Reilly 系列 Web 服务器产品。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1180"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.360","remediation":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e/Website Pro 2.0 已停止维护，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx），并彻底停止使用旧版软件。如无法立即迁移，可在 Web 服务器前端部署 WAF 规则拦截包含 shell 元字符（如 `;`、`|`、`&`、反引号）的请求，并对 `args.cmd`、`args.bat` 参数输入进行严格白名单过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/buffer.html","http://www.tryc.on.ca/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0612.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1180","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1180.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/args_bat.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88632/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000527.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/args_bat.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0375","title":"Network Flight Recorder webd 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Network Flight Recorder (NFR) 2.0.2-Research 版本的 webd 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份验证即可通过网络向 webd 服务发送特制请求，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以服务进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，可导致机密性、完整性和可用性完全受损。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0375"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-16","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"NFR 2.0.2-Research 已停止维护，建议升级到厂商后续安全版本或迁移至替代网络监控方案。如无法升级，应在网络边界防火墙限制对 webd 服务端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0375","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0375"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1260","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 信息泄露漏洞","description":"mSQL（Mini SQL）2.0.6 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过发送 ServerStats 查询请求，未经验证的远程用户即可获取服务器的敏感信息，包括当前在线用户列表、数据库名称以及服务器版本等关键数据。该漏洞源于 mSQL 2.0.6 对 ServerStats 查询的权限验证不足，导致攻击者能够轻易提取数据库服务器的详细配置信息和运行状态，对数据库系统的安全性和隐私性造成严重威胁。该漏洞可通过简单的网络请求触发，无需任何特殊权限即可执行，从而为攻击者提供了大量关于目标系统内部结构的敏感信息，有可能进一步为后续攻击行动提供支持。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1260"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.557","remediation":"升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本，以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91910115718150&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1777","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1260","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87764/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0311","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0714","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX edauth 命令漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 操作系统的 edauth 命令存在权限管理缺陷，本地攻击者无需额外认证即可利用该命令读取系统上的敏感文件，导致机密信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0714"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-02-15","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Compaq（现 HP）已针对 Tru64 UNIX 的 edauth 命令漏洞发布安全补丁，建议用户联系厂商获取对应操作系统版本的补丁程序，或升级到已修复该漏洞的 Tru64 UNIX 版本。由于该产品已停止主流支持，建议迁移至受支持的替代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0714","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0714"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0043","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0404","title":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 SMTP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 的 SMTP 服务组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 25 端口发送特制的超长 SMTP 命令触发该漏洞，导致目标系统拒绝服务或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台下的 MailMax 1.0 版本，无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。厂商未提供官方补丁，建议停止使用该软件或通过防火墙限制 SMTP 端口的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0404"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.490","remediation":"升级 SmartMax MailMax 至 2.0 或更高版本。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的邮件服务器软件，并在防火墙中限制 SMTP 端口（25/TCP）仅允许可信来源访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0404","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20600","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0404","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0404.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/310.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/mailmax_imap_overflows.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0404.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0612","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0372","title":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 4.0 安装程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 4.0 安装程序在安装 SQL Server、Exchange Server 或 Microsoft Transaction Server 时，会要求用户输入相关服务账户名和密码，并将这些凭据以明文形式写入 <systemdrive>\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini 文件中。安装完成后（无论成功与否），该文件未被自动删除。本地攻击者若能登录服务器，即可读取该文件获取明文账户密码，进而利用获取的凭据提升权限或访问受保护资源。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0372"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-02-12","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装完成后手动删除 <systemdrive>\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini 文件，该文件仅由安装程序创建，删除后不会自动重建。建议在每次 BackOffice Server 4.0 安装完成后（无论成功与否）立即删除此文件，防止本地攻击者读取明文账户密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ217004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-005"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0611","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0371","title":"Lynx lynx 本地符号链接敏感文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Lynx 文本浏览器在处理临时文件时存在不安全的符号链接跟踪漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 /tmp 目录下预创建指向目标敏感文件的符号链接，诱导 Lynx 将临时数据写入该链接指向的文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件，导致数据破坏或权限提升。利用条件为攻击者拥有本地账户权限且 Lynx 以当前用户权限运行。该漏洞影响早期版本 Lynx，CVSS 评分 1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0371"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.167","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.7.1 或更高版本，该版本已改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免预测 /tmp 路径导致的竞争条件。如无法升级，确保 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod 1777 /tmp），并通过设置环境变量 TMPDIR 指向用户私有临时目录来缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0371"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml"}]